titles.title: Requesting the Senate to return to the House of Representatives the bill H.R. 2217.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 6/11/2013--Introduced. Directs the Clerk of the House of Representatives to request the Senate to return to the House H.R. 2217 (Department of Homeland Security Appropriations Act, 2014).
